      "date": "2015-07-31 09:09:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/7f9a4840-3762-11e5-a8a9-5254006e85c2).  Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
